#### 缓存实现

##### Next.js Cache (unstable_cache)

```
const storyblokApiFetch = unstable_cache(
  async () => {
    return await storyblokApi.get(`cdn/stories/${slug}`, {
      version: isTest ? 'draft' : 'published',
      cv: getTimestamp(),
    });
  },
  [`${slug}`],
  {
    tags: [`${slug}`],
    revalidate: EcEnv.NEXT_PUBLIC_STORYBLOK_REVALIDATE_TIME,
  }
);
```

##### React Cache（请求去重）

```
// libs/modules/cms/services/src/lib/sbBaseService.ts

// React Cache 用于请求去重，同一请求生命周期内复用结果
private cachedGetStory = reactCache(async <T>(slug: string, params?: Partial<ISbStoryParams>) => {
  return this.getStory<T>(slug, params);
});

// React Cache + Next.js Cache 组合使用
private cachedGetStoryWithPersistentCache = reactCache(
  async <T>(slug: string, params?: Partial<ISbStoryParams>, options?: {...}) => {
    return this.getStoryWithCache<T>(slug, params, options); // 内部使用 Next.js Cache
  }
);
```

##### 使用场景

- getStoryWithReactCache：仅使用 React Cache（请求去重，无持久化）
- getStoryWithBothCache：React Cache + Next.js Cache（请求去重，持久化）
